@{fg shine}There's more!@{fg text}

 If you want the latest version of Connexion (assuming I do another
one), and you have access to the internet, you can look on the Anarchy 
Software Amiga home page, located at the following address...

 @{fg highlight}http://www.nebula.demon.co.uk/anarchy/@{fg text}

 If I do release another major update, I will probably upload it to the
Aminet, but any minor changes (little bug fixes and tweaks) will only be
uploaded to the above page.  The date and version of each game will be
shown on the home page so that you'll be able to tell if the version
